{
  "stem": "5551.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That is that infamous camp that is represented in that movie.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The-- the-- the commander, the commandant, of this camp was a man by the name of Goeth.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He was truly sub-human.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He was a murderous character.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "When we came to Goeth, we were lined up, and they were counting one, two, three.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "My father was one, I was two, and a boy behind me that I knew well, a wonderful Jewish boy from Gorlice, was three.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Everybody who was three was pulled aside.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We were-- we were made to understand that there is not enough place for all of us, so one third of us will have to be liquidated.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They were taken aside-- it was purely by one, two, three-- they were taken aside, and they had-- you must forgive me.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I know you speak Polish, [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was a place-- it is a derogatory place of a hill that they used for killings.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we heard the machine guns killing these people right away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So every third one was taken out of the-- as we came into this murderous camp by-- again, the main killing was done by the Ukrainians, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] under German supervision.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Of course, the Germans gave them the orders and supervised them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In any event, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] every third one was taken out and murdered by machine gun fire.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We could hear the machine gun fire.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We could not see the action, but we were soon told where it took place and how it took place by those who were in the camp and who knew that this is routine at the [NON-ENGLISH] in-- in Goeth's camp.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We spend over there only a few days.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
